<br />

<br />
I'm trying to find the fastest way possible to get AA's. I'm not really a fan of AE kiting because with R3 I manage to get hit still, plus Extended Notes don't work anymore with it... I'm perfectly up to soloing though - IE swarming, chanting ... etc.
<br />

<br />
I've been killing in tactics lately making about 2-3 a night, and 4-6 in a day's work, but I know there has to be faster out there.
<br />

<br />
I could use any suggestions,
<br />
Thanks!</span></td>
